column5: Nice rig Terry!!!
Nice job boys!  Surprised the fish weren't scared of that hat/shirt combo Brian was wearing
thanks all  if you think that shirt is busy, wait till you see the one he wears today,,,,lol
Awesome boat man! Congrats!!

Terrys new boat is sweet The 125 opti, really moves this machine.  The happy new owner.      Fishing started of tough. Took a bit to get the first fish,but once the first fish came in,Terry was on a roll.  First fish in the new boat,and caught by the capt himself.    Followed by another      And another  [/url]  And so on         Oh,I got one too.LOL       Nice rig buddy.
it was great to get out flipping them banks  everything worked , nothing broke and we caught fish  sounds like a good day to me  now the boat is slimed  glad it wasn't that bowfin slime...lol
LOL That was a bigg,n.I wont mention those catfish ok. LOL
yeah, I got a little catfish slime on her too
Great stuff guys.  That really is a sweet ride Terry.  Glad you slimed her for the first time.  A virgin no more
Hey terry, how did you end up installing the tracks on the gunwales?  Congrats again on the new baby
Great job guys,Terry looks like the new ride is a bass magnet. You two came pretty close to us but by the time I noticed you were given'r,and too late lol.
Were you sitting in the mouth Dave?
Yes, the wind was blowing us north east.You two weren't 100' away. Managed a solid 3lb and a couple 1 1/2lb..Lot of other fish caught but not very big.
Sweet ride, sweet day... cant ask for much more!
Glad it worked out well, Terry. Beautiful boat....nice shirt too!
Terry even managed to catch this one. It was blind in one eye.       Thanks LOL
dress for success   hey got a temp fix for riggers...how tomorrow Bri
Oh ya,lets GREASE her now.................. That didnt sound right,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
Awesome guys. Congrats on sliming the new rig Terry.
thanks guys  it was great  to fish out of it...tomorrow lakers
Beautiful boat Terry!
Guess the mail must be slow..... all I got yesterday was an invite to my nephews wedding! )  Good to see it slimed Terry... makes up for some of the hair pulling of waiting for her to come in!
The "nice shirt" award of this post goes to Brian. He could wear that shirt out all day fishing and then straight to the gumboot clogaroo without changing.
lol
LMAO.. now that's a hook set!
a little too hard...lol if it was 6lbs that would barely turn it around
Glad to see you enjoying your new rig...
That shirt is what attracted the fish!  LOL!
Atta boy Terry, cocngrats on the new boat !!
